Microfiche. New Delhi : Library of Congress Office ; Washington, D.C. : Library of Congress Photoduplication Service, 1993-    microfiches <52-   >.
A collection of pamphlets on Ayurveda, family medicine, diet therapy, and healing powers of nature, published during 1988-1992.
Contents list arranged alphabetically by title. Includes index by author/editor and title, and series, author/editor, and title.
Additional materials with other dates of publication may be found in this collection.
Collected and organized by the Library of Congress Office, New Delhi.
Master microform held by: DLC.
